  "description": "<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<strong><span style=\"color: #006400;\">今日知识点 ---&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">weight 和 weighting 的区别你知道吗？&nbsp;</span></span></strong></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<img src=\"https://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/10/27/d963913e726a81840faa9f81651b79bd.png\" /></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">在英语中，大家应该都非常熟悉 weight 这个词吧？没错，它是&ldquo;重量&rdquo;的意思。</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t但是，如果在weight后面加上ing，你知道是什么意思吗？</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tweighting 可做名词，也可做形容词，是一个在商务英语中非常重要的词。</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t做名词的时候，基本意思由 weight 引申而来，weighting 表示 &ldquo;加重，加权&rdquo;。</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t比如：</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span style=\"color: #006400;\">weighting function &nbsp;</span>加权函数 ; 权重函数</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span style=\"color: #006400;\">weighting coefficient</span> 加权系数</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span style=\"color: #006400;\">weighting factor</span> 权重因数</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span style=\"color: #006400;\">item weighting</span> 项目加权 ; 项权重</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t但如果用作形容词，weighting 表示<span style=\"color: #006400;\"> &ldquo;额外的&rdquo; &ldquo;增重的&rdquo; </span>意思，比如：</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span style=\"color: #006400;\">weighting allowance</span> 额外津贴</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span style=\"color: #006400;\">weighting &nbsp;agent </span>增重剂，填充剂</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span style=\"color: #006400;\">weighting characteristic</span> 加权特征</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<img src=\"https://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/10/27/8489df08efa45bf1bab04a20d8370e9e.png\" /></div>\n<div id=\"c